In addition to searches for specific languages, additional searches that might be of
           interest are Haggadot with commentaries by a specific commentator, such as Abarbanel; with wine
              stains;
           signed by someone; with music;
           handwritten;
           illustrated; are a certain size, such as 17 cm; from a specific city; illustrated by a specific
           artist; etc.

did.unittitle:
Hagadah shel Pesah : Tri'esti 624 = The Passover
  Haggadah : Trieste 1864 / mahadurat Avraham Hai Morpurgo ;
  ha-ilustratsyot `a. y. K. Krikhmayer [sic],  1864.

scopecontent.p:
English translation by Betzalel Ruth. Illustrated and decorated by Albert
                        Rutherston. Issued in gold-stamped blue crushed morocco; all edges gilt;
                        signed inside front cover: Bound by Wood, London.

